title: All Champions Level 5 Mastery.
body: Hey so, I was just curious as to whether or not anyone has actually managed to get all of them? I mean to be fair it probably isn't that common based on champ preference but is there anyone out there with all if not most?

replies.body: Damn! 50 is heaps. I only have 14 at the moment :P

I'm sad i play everyone so i don't focus on getting champion mastery i just play what ever i feel like, but anyway i currently have 5 level 5s xD but i have 16 level 4s and 31 level 3s so yeah i play everyone haha. Feelsbadman with a 290 mastery score

Yea I know the feeling. I only ever play what I feel like at that particular moment. But yea I only have 14 level 5's, 9 level 4's, 35 level 3's. With 3 of the level 4's over half way to level 5 and 17 of the level 3's over half way to level 4. So I play a wide variety also and I tend to have like 10 game streaks on a particular champion.
